---
title: Chinese Pork Meatballs with Udon Noodles & Crispy Shallots
description: This saucy noodle number puts a tasty Asian twist on meatballs and spaghetti. Tender pork meatballs and Asian greens are
coated in a mouth-watering char siu glaze, with a sprinkling of crispy shallots for crunch.
